28099C                   KFLD                    p6arti                                             
28099C                   KFLD                    p6vari                                             
28099C                   KFLD                    p6mode                                             
28099C                   KFLD                    p6unim                                             
28099                                                                                               
FQ284C     KCODIPE       KLIST                                                                      
FQ284C                   KFLD                    S2CIAS                                             
FQ284C                   KFLD                    S2DLGA                                             
FQ284C                   KFLD                    S2NPCO                                             
FQ284C                   KFLD                    S2TPED                                             
FQ284C                   KFLD                    S2DATP                                             
FQ284C                   KFLD                    S2NOPL                                             
FQ284C                   KFLD                    S2CDIR                                             
