FQ284C                   CALL      'UT2570'                                                         
FQ284C                   PARM                    @PECADENA                                          
FQ284C                   PARM      '2'           @PEACCION                                          
FQ284C                   PARM      *BLANKS       @PEERROR                                           
FQ284 *                                                                                             
FQ284C                   IF        @PEERROR=*BLANKS                                                 
FQ284C                   EVAL      WK_S2RAOS=@PECADENA                                              
